<collectingRegion box="[264,379,251,275]" country="Russia" name="Saint Petersburg" pageId="21" pageNumber="608">Petersburg</collectingRegion>
from where it was borrowed by Zachary Falin (
<collectingRegion box="[871,948,252,276]" country="United States of America" name="Kansas" pageId="21" pageNumber="608">Kansas</collectingRegion>
) in 1999.
</paragraph>
